TgVoipWebrtc is built from Telegram's Telegram-iOS and tgcalls sources.

The tgcalls sources are licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License,
version 3. The corresponding source and full license are available at:
https://github.com/TelegramMessenger/tgcalls

The exact Telegram-iOS source revision used by Mithka's build script is
recorded in docs/group-calls-ios.md.
